data.title: About: Shock to the System (Gemma Hayes song)
data.meta_description: "Shock To The System" is a song written by Irish singer-songwriter Gemma Hayes for her fourth studio album Let It Break. It was the first single released from this album in May 2011 in Ireland. The single was released in Internationally as a single on 15 May 2012.
data.text:
dbo:abstract

"Shock To The System" is a song written by Irish singer-songwriter Gemma Hayes for her fourth studio album Let It Break. It was the first single released from this album in May 2011 in Ireland. The single was released in Internationally as a single on 15 May 2012. (en)
